user_text: Old school Italian pizzeria. Authentic sauce and dough 5 stars. Worth the price and great value. Don't expect the Ritz Carlton bozo. And be respectful this is an old Mom and Pop store.
I love their pizza! I love their wings.... So good!!!!!!!!!! Went here all throughout high school and they haven't changed a bit. Nice local spot to get a slice, yum yum yum.
Real authentic Italian food. I love the pizza. It's real and made fresh.i love this place alot you should try it if you didnt. It makes my life happy and full of taste.
The pizza here is very greasy and tastes good its the establishment itself which is gross everything is dusty and i have even seen spider webs.
Typical NY/NJ-Italian pizza joint.  Pizza is greasy, but tasty.  They also have free delivery.
